      "name": "Small Red Potatoes",
      "amount": "1 lb (450g)"
    },
    {
      "name": "Olive Oil",
      "amount": "2 tbsp"
    },
    {
      "name": "Garlic Cloves",
      "amount": "2 cloves, minced"
    },
    {
      "name": "Red Chili Flakes",
      "amount": "1 tsp"
    },
    {
      "name": "Fresh Parsley",
      "amount": "1/4 cup, chopped (optional)"
    },
    {
      "name": "Coarse Sea Salt",
      "amount": "1 tsp"
    }
  ],
  "instructions": [
    "Preheat your grill to medium-high heat.",
    "Peel and halve the potatoes. Coat them lightly with olive oil and sprinkle with coarse sea salt.",
    "Grill the potatoes until they're charred, about 5-7 minutes per side.",
    "Add minced garlic and red chili flakes to a small mixing bowl and toss together.",
    "Once the potatoes are cooked, slice them in half lengthwise. Top each half with the spicy garlic mixture and fresh parsley (if using).",
    "Serve immediately for best texture."
  ],
